  │  
  │  *   **Empty `list1`:** If `list1` is empty (`n1 == 0`), the main loop won't execute. The code will correctly proceed to append all elements from `list2`.
  │  *   **Empty `list2`:** If `list2` is empty (`n2 == 0`), the main loop won't execute. The code will correctly proceed to append all elements from `list1`.
